WEBVTT

00:13:59.882 --> 00:14:01.945
on a system that does not want us.

00:14:01.969 --> 00:14:05.575
We need to find our audience
and invest in cultivating them.

00:14:05.599 --> 00:14:07.832
If we can figure out
how to make our movies

00:14:07.856 --> 00:14:10.340
and deliver them
to the audiences that want them,

00:14:10.364 --> 00:14:11.524
that's it.

00:14:11.548 --> 00:14:12.913
That's the whole game.

00:14:12.937 --> 00:14:14.903
And whatever they're doing in the middle

00:14:14.927 --> 00:14:17.198
is going to cease to be
quite so important.

00:14:17.222 --> 00:14:19.682
Audiences, invest in us.

00:14:20.293 --> 00:14:23.231
Help us make the movies
that you want to see.

00:14:23.255 --> 00:14:27.194
If you can give a female filmmaker
25 dollars in a crowdfunding campaign,

00:14:27.218 --> 00:14:28.494
great, do that.

00:14:28.518 --> 00:14:30.115
If you can invest more seriously